message.body: Do you have or have access to that canned air stuff with a straw that I can use some of?
Yeah- do you want it tonight? I'm going to swing by the suite later and i can bring it. We're doing catan in ryan at the moment.
I brought you the stuff. It's in the common room. You can leave the payment in the usual location.
Man I might have to pay you later...the price of air just keeps getting higher and higher these days
You gonna be good for it? This is high quality air. Stuff like this doesn't come easy.
Oh I'm good for it. Don't worry I totally understand...it's a diminishing resource
